[{"url_token": "haiqi-cai", "headline": "走更远的路，见更大的世界", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "732631717", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "答主果然是新手，开车居然看内后视镜的次数比后视镜多，你这驾照需要回炉重考啊，上路就是马路杀手级别。我开车十几年，几乎不看内后视镜，通过两边的后视镜的完全可以观察出周边所有的路况，还有开车主要看的是前面和侧面而不是正后方", "like_count": 44, "author_name": "小九", "author_id": "b3eef3fc36e4843f7a5b1bdb339d039b", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "wo-tou-hong-shao-rou", "headline": "跨界工程师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2513686278", "reply_comment_id": "2510541975", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "开车尽可能“眼观六路耳听八方”，养成即使正向行驶也经常扫一眼内后视镜的习惯，做到对前后左右车辆动态都了然于胸，这其实很重要。我没法强迫你立即认同，但随着时间推移，你早晚会理解的。<br><br>我不确定知道现在驾校都怎么教，但听说过一些，感觉比二十多年前教的少，我那时教练讲了很多行车经验，当时感觉没什么用，后来才发现，那都是升级版的教学内容，新手基本用不上，年头越多越感觉，教练讲得真特么的对。", "like_count": 14, "author_name": "窝头红烧肉", "author_id": "0f25f6175499e27faaee88dc9744c4fa", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wo-tou-hong-shao-rou", "headline": "跨界工程师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2511139873", "reply_comment_id": "2439825963", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "从不看内后视镜，绝对不是好习惯，难道厂家多余安装这么个玩意？", "like_count": 7, "author_name": "窝头红烧肉", "author_id": "0f25f6175499e27faaee88dc9744c4fa", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "boxkong", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4314308959", "reply_comment_id": "2513686278", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "非常支持你的看法，车内后视镜非常重要。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "Box控", "author_id": "d220a43107f3b5595aab006fb577d8a3", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wo-tou-hong-shao-rou", "headline": "跨界工程师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10090846148", "reply_comment_id": "10090522576", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "雨天车多时，真心危险", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "窝头红烧肉", "author_id": "0f25f6175499e27faaee88dc9744c4fa", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yun-xiao-xiao-12-53", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10121861226", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我新手五千公里，我也觉得内后视镜非常重要。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "云潇潇", "author_id": "227bd2bfed8f80bd5f12d3ba054f879f", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zui-ji-zhi-de-guang-6", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4623204671", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "正常行车就是应该多看车内后视镜，车外那两个在变道转弯倒车的时候用处才大。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "最极致的光", "author_id": "46f223acf2edde1c74f01a8f8f4b99ad", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zui-ji-zhi-de-guang-6", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4623025798", "reply_comment_id": "4617144459", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "自己去看看车内后视镜的视野吧。以后开车对比一下三个镜子。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "最极致的光", "author_id": "46f223acf2edde1c74f01a8f8f4b99ad", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "haiqi-cai", "headline": "走更远的路，见更大的世界", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4617144459", "reply_comment_id": "4623204671", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "没想到马路上这么多新手。正常行驶最重要的是观察前左右的路况做到心中有数，因为紧急变道的时候根本来不及看左右后视镜，你看内后视镜有什么用？数你后面有多少车吗？", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "小九", "author_id": "b3eef3fc36e4843f7a5b1bdb339d039b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "mei-nei-de-si-35", "headline": "无需介绍", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2544497603", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你这个回复充分说明了你很菜，不要再说别人菜了，正视一下自己", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "无敌小狗头", "author_id": "2e29fceffccaf9b7453465ac88f93e4e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yin-shi-zi-hei-qi-shi", "headline": "心里有座坟，埋着未亡人……", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2439825963", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "正解，我也不看内后视镜，左右后视镜就足以看到后方车辆了。<br>而且，把内后视镜掰歪还能防止后面的远光狗闪瞎眼（一定程度上）[飙泪笑]", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "银十字黑骑士", "author_id": "1e774cf4faaaf41fab6ab925ac82e9bb", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhen-ai-bao-bei-er", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2619137679", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "内后视镜方便，不用转头，抬抬眼皮就看到了哈哈，但是我是属于那种都看的，用到哪个看哪个[大笑]", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "珍爱宝贝儿", "author_id": "f07523aa2db4910baea80aa1fc8c2423", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wo-tou-hong-shao-rou", "headline": "跨界工程师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4315828644", "reply_comment_id": "2551035949", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "你的逻辑太幽默了。<br><br>我倒车时，会看倒车影像，会听倒车雷达提醒。要是没有雷达和影像，我就不倒车了吗？当然不是，没有影像和雷达，我一样倒车技术不错，但是影像和雷达效果更好。<br><br>内后视镜也一样，没它不是绝对不行，但有了更好。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "窝头红烧肉", "author_id": "0f25f6175499e27faaee88dc9744c4fa", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "haiqi-cai", "headline": "走更远的路，见更大的世界", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2551035949", "reply_comment_id": "2544497603", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "厢式货车的内后视镜只能用来照镜子，你们这样的司机估计开不了吧。不会开车没关系，可以去学个驾照花不了几个钱", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "小九", "author_id": "b3eef3fc36e4843f7a5b1bdb339d039b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "mei-nei-de-si-35", "headline": "无需介绍", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10165010614", "reply_comment_id": "10164599416", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "那厂家设计内后视镜是让你化妆用的吗", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "无敌小狗头", "author_id": "2e29fceffccaf9b7453465ac88f93e4e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "zhou-miao-miao-79-68", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10164599416", "reply_comment_id": "2544497603", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这话你自己适用，内后视镜根本用不上懂吗？习惯看左右外后视镜才是真相", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "喵喵", "author_id": "16161aac970a30f599b920cce8d2f44b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "gao-xiao-niu-4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10149993996", "reply_comment_id": "732631717", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "[大笑][大笑]三个镜子都看吧，没有中间那个镜子心里总不放心。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "高小牛", "author_id": "186277d5a88e675021f235975bf70568", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "haiqi-cai", "headline": "走更远的路，见更大的世界", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10122180828", "reply_comment_id": "10121861226", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "要不然怎么是新手呢，我十几年驾龄三十几万公里，开过厢式货车，内后视镜只能看到车厢，按你们的说法这种车不能上路了吧", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "小九", "author_id": "b3eef3fc36e4843f7a5b1bdb339d039b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "feng-zhong-de-gou-wei-cao-72", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10090522576", "reply_comment_id": "2511139873", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我就试过一次晚上下雨跑高速，后面跟着一台黑色的车，后面又全是灯光，我就是只看了两侧后视镜，没看内后视镜差点就怼了别人。确实要看清楚这些后视镜再行动。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "风中的狗尾草", "author_id": "66b95552c931fbc919881c841cd1916e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "she-ying-huang", "headline": "地质调查与找矿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4673415049", "reply_comment_id": "4672533981", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "还是有用的，比如说看看后面的美女帅哥，养眼呗[飙泪笑][飙泪笑]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "蛇樱皇", "author_id": "064cf02be7c30e6affc5fb260cd1a20b", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yin-shi-zi-hei-qi-shi", "headline": "心里有座坟，埋着未亡人……", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "4673130300", "reply_comment_id": "4673415049", "reply_root_comment_id": "732631717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "啊对，我平时都是用内后视镜看副驾的媳妇[捂嘴]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "银十字黑骑士", "author_id": "1e774cf4faaaf41fab6ab925ac82e9bb", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "heagle-tsin", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "684807253", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "684807253", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "跟你一样，我觉得车内镜很实用，后座尽量不让人坐中间。凯迪拉克的流媒体后视镜让我很难受，自己加装成了普通镜子", "like_count": 7, "author_name": "听君一席话", "author_id": "5c4c2751165990ec53ce7b2771564ae6", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "yin-shi-zi-hei-qi-shi", "headline": "心里有座坟，埋着未亡人……", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2439705960", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "2439705960", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我加油都是油表灯亮再加", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "银十字黑骑士", "author_id": "1e774cf4faaaf41fab6ab925ac82e9bb", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "yin-shi-zi-hei-qi-shi", "headline": "心里有座坟，埋着未亡人……", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2650485921", "reply_comment_id": "2646677659", "reply_root_comment_id": "2439705960", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "汽油量少确实会让油泵运转压力变大，但是我觉得没啥事，我09款睿翼的日本进口油泵应该没这么脆弱吧[好奇]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "银十字黑骑士", "author_id": "1e774cf4faaaf41fab6ab925ac82e9bb", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shuai-zha-liao-de-ge-ge", "headline": "帅的掉渣哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2646677659", "reply_comment_id": "2439705960", "reply_root_comment_id": "2439705960", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "百度地图app推送说长时间等报警再加油会造成油泵发热损坏，我觉得很多道理[思考]，但是我选择续驶里程50以下再加[大笑]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "帅炸了的哥哥", "author_id": "3d6368a368e6308b24b5748a861e0011", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "volley47", "headline": "一位平平无奇的男士", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "890394941", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "890394941", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我妈给买的保平安的小物件我都放在手套箱里😂😂😂", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "王俊杰", "author_id": "75c7a41b7d27ee80a34c01257cbf3923", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "shuai-zha-liao-de-ge-ge", "headline": "帅的掉渣哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2646917504", "reply_comment_id": "890394941", "reply_root_comment_id": "890394941", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "哈哈不，我放扶手箱[思考]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "帅炸了的哥哥", "author_id": "3d6368a368e6308b24b5748a861e0011", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "shuai-zha-liao-de-ge-ge", "headline": "帅的掉渣哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2646407705", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "2646407705", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "第七条深有感触[思考]有时候暗到都想把膜撕掉的冲动，所以机智的我一般选择摇下车窗[思考]", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "帅炸了的哥哥", "author_id": "3d6368a368e6308b24b5748a861e0011", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "dong-tian-de-yu-42-76", "headline": "无业游民，曾做过汽车销售，快递员，对汽车驾驶